Introduction
************

   Welcome to the GNU @{b}tar@{ub} manual.  GNU @{b}tar@{ub} is used to create and
manipulate files (@{i}archives@{ui}) which are actually collections of many
other files; the program provides users with an organized and
systematic method for controlling a large amount of data.


